01:03:26,201 --> 01:03:27,964
- Grayer: Get away from me!
- Oh, sweetheart.

1306
01:03:28,003 --> 01:03:30,403
Don't be afraid.
They're only clowns.

1307
01:03:30,438 --> 01:03:32,235
- I hate them.
- They're nice French clowns.

1308
01:03:32,274 --> 01:03:35,175
