1320
01:03:59,167 --> 01:04:02,466
...starting Thursday evening.

1321
01:04:02,504 --> 01:04:05,371
Do you read to the child
from "The Wall Street Journal"?

1322
01:04:05,440 --> 01:04:08,409
"Financial Times"?
"Granta"?

1323
01:04:09,644 --> 01:04:11,612
[jungle sounds]

1324
01:04:11,647 --> 01:04:14,081
I-- I sing to him
in French.

1325
01:04:14,115 --> 01:04:17,516
Well, we need more time
than I thought

1326
01:04:17,552 --> 01:04:19,417
to get to
the bottom of this.

1327
01:04:19,454 --> 01:04:21,115
[horn honking]

1328
01:04:24,392 --> 01:04:26,223
[sighs]

1329
01:04:27,495 --> 01:04:29,861
I know.
I know, I'm very very late.

1330
01:04:29,899 --> 01:04:31,662
I'm sorry.
Did you get my message?

1331
01:04:31,701 --> 01:04:34,295
- Yep. All six of 'em.
- I couldn't get out of work.

1332
01:04:34,336 --> 01:04:36,804
