1338
01:04:49,150 --> 01:04:52,415
Wait, whoa whoa whoa
whoa whoa whoa whoa.

1339
01:04:52,454 --> 01:04:54,718
Think you can just get
rid of me that easily?

1340
01:04:54,757 --> 01:04:56,588
No, it's not about
getting rid of you.

