imagining you in Harlem.

1352
01:05:32,728 --> 01:05:35,925
Why? I enjoy
exploring my city.

1353
01:05:35,965 --> 01:05:37,762
Something you should
probably do more of.

1354
01:05:37,800 --> 01:05:39,665
Oh, thank you.

1355
01:05:39,702 --> 01:05:42,967
I'll try to squeeze that in between
cleaning up Grayer's vomit

1356
01:05:43,004 --> 01:05:44,733
and picking up
Mrs. X's laundry.

1357
01:05:44,774 --> 01:05:47,470
Come on, if your job is that bad,
why don't you just quit?

1358
01:05:47,509 --> 01:05:49,807
I mean, it's not like you're on
a career path here.

1359
01:05:49,845 --> 01:05:51,073
I don't understand.

1360
01:05:51,112 --> 01:05:52,739
No, of course
you don't understand.

1361
01:05:52,782 --> 01:05:55,410
You've obviously lived
a very charmed life

1362
01:05:55,450 --> 01:05:58,180
growing up on Fifth Avenue.
You went to Harvard.

1363
01:05:58,219 --> 01:06:00,153
