nine different nannies

1369
01:06:15,938 --> 01:06:18,429
until I was old enough
to get shipped off to boarding school.

1370
01:06:18,473 --> 01:06:20,873
That's how charmed
my life was.

1371
01:06:25,313 --> 01:06:27,577
- I'm really sorry.
- But you know something?

1372
01:06:27,616 --> 01:06:29,777
