I can do?

1533
01:15:15,643 --> 01:15:18,339
Just close the door.

1534
01:15:26,855 --> 01:15:29,085
[sighs]

1535
01:15:29,123 --> 01:15:30,590
He's okay now.

1536
01:15:30,625 --> 01:15:32,252
Much better.

1537
01:15:32,293 --> 01:15:33,760
Oh, thank you, God.

1538
01:15:33,795 --> 01:15:36,263
