from living one.

1590
01:18:08,984 --> 01:18:12,420
Clearly, the woman's
heinous.

1591
01:18:12,453 --> 01:18:14,648
You gotta quit.
It's just that simple.

1592
01:18:14,690 --> 01:18:17,557
I can't, all right?
I tried.

1593
01:18:17,591 --> 01:18:20,924
What if I made you
a tempting offer?

1594
01:18:20,962 --> 01:18:23,954
I'm gonna go to my father's house in
Southampton for a month.

1595
01:18:23,999 --> 01:18:28,459
I've got to take some time, figure out
if law school is really right for me.

1596
01:18:28,502 --> 01:18:29,867
Why don't you join me?

1597
01:18:29,905 --> 01:18:31,998
Do a little soul-searching.

1598
01:18:32,039 --> 01:18:34,371
We'd get the whole house to ourselves--
won't cost us a cent.

1599
01:18:34,408 --> 01:18:37,605
We'll walk on the beach.
We'll drink red wine,

1600
01:18:37,645 --> 01:18:40,079
grill fresh fish.

1601
01:18:40,114 --> 01:18:43,572
That sounds like heaven.

1602
01:18:43,617 --> 01:18:46,051
But what if this vacation
can save their marriage?

1603
01:18:46,087 --> 01:18:48,248
If I quit now,
I'll ruin it

1604
01:18:48,289 --> 01:18:50,120
and break Grayer's heart.

1605
01:18:50,157 --> 01:18:53,490
What about my heart?
Do I count for anything?

1606
01:18:55,630 --> 01:18:58,531
Come on, say yes.

1607
01:18:58,566 --> 01:19:01,000
Be young with me
in the Hamptons.

1608
01:19:01,035 --> 01:19:03,560
Don't go to Nantucket
with the weirdoes.

1609
01:19:03,604 --> 01:19:05,731
What do you say?

1610
01:19:14,515 --> 01:19:17,484
Not a chance in hell
is there?

1611
01:19:17,518 --> 01:19:20,453
- I can take a hint.
- Come on, I didn't say no.

1612
01:19:20,488 --> 01:19:23,616
You weren't exactly screaming
yes though, were you?

1613
01:19:23,657 --> 01:19:25,682
I'm starting to wonder
if you're really selfless

1614
01:19:25,726 --> 01:19:28,388
or just a little
self-obsessed.

1615
01:19:28,429 --> 01:19:30,329
Thank you.
Thanks.

1616
01:19:30,364 --> 01:19:32,798
I have to go.

1617
01:19:35,269 --> 01:19:39,638
Listen, if you change
your mind, my offer stands.

1618
01:19:46,948 --> 01:19:49,348
Grayer: We're going to 'Tucket.
We're going to 'Tucket.

1619
01:19:49,383 --> 01:19:52,648
Guess what else?
I'm getting a puppy.

1620
01:19:52,686 --> 01:19:54,813
- [plane rattles]
- Oh!

1621
01:19:54,855 --> 01:19:57,016
- Oh my God!
- [Grayer laughs]

1622
01:19:59,326 --> 01:20:02,090
Daddy, Daddy,
where's my puppy?

1623
01:20:02,129 --> 01:20:05,496
Been waiting for you right up
in the car there, sport.

1624
01:20:05,533 --> 01:20:07,296
- Isn't it wonderful?
- Mmm.

1625
01:20:07,334 --> 01:20:09,427
A family trip has been
long overdue.

1626
01:20:09,470 --> 01:20:12,200
Mmm, listen, I didn't
want to say anything in front of Grayer,

1627
01:20:12,239 --> 01:20:14,207
but the truth is,
I can only stay for a few days.

1628
01:20:14,241 --> 01:20:16,937
They're really pushing me to
finish up in Chicago.

1629
01:20:16,978 --> 01:20:19,503
You can't be serious.

1630
01:20:19,547 --> 01:20:21,515
You're not gonna leave us
on this island alone.

1631
01:20:21,549 --> 01:20:23,608
Okay, we'll talk
about it later.

1632
01:20:23,651 --> 01:20:26,313
#  But I'm moving on # 

1633
