doesn't work here.

1641
01:20:50,010 --> 01:20:52,774
So if you wanted
to call--

1642
01:20:52,813 --> 01:20:55,179
if you wanted
to call

1643
01:20:55,216 --> 01:20:57,343
- you probably have the number...
- Grayer: Nanny, hurry up!

1644
01:20:57,384 --> 01:20:59,352
...already on your cell phone,
but I will give it to you

1645
01:20:59,386 --> 01:21:02,219
just in case.
It is 508...

1646
01:21:02,256 --> 01:21:04,486
- Mrs. X: Hello?
- Oh.

1647
01:21:04,525 --> 01:21:06,652
- What, hello?
- Hello, Nanny?

1648
01:21:06,695 --> 01:21:08,390
- Wha...
- I need to use this phone.

1649
01:21:08,429 --> 01:21:10,829
- Immediately.
- Okay, so sorry.

1650
01:21:10,866 --> 01:21:14,495
- Oh God.
- Nanny, we're going to the beach.

1651
01:21:14,535 --> 01:21:16,901
When I grow up,
I want enough money

1652
01:21:16,938 --> 01:21:19,338
to build a real castle.

1653
01:21:19,373 --> 01:21:22,536
Just remember, Grove,
that money can't buy love.

1654
01:21:22,577 --> 01:21:25,569
But Mommy pays you money
and I love you.

1655
01:21:25,614 --> 01:21:28,276
Woman:
Surprise surprise, dear.

1656
01:21:30,084 --> 01:21:33,952
- Mother?
- My, you've gotten portly.

1657
01:21:33,989 --> 01:21:36,480
Hi, Grandma.

1658
01:21:36,523 --> 01:21:38,650
What the hell
are you doing here?

1659
01:21:38,692 --> 01:21:42,423
Ask your wife.
She's the one who requested I come.

1660
01:21:42,463 --> 01:21:46,092
- Darling, I--
- Not that I need an invitation.

1661
01:21:46,133 --> 01:21:48,260
It is my house.

1662
01:21:48,302 --> 01:21:50,770
I just wanted your mother
to be here for the news.

1663
01:21:50,805 --> 01:21:53,433
News, what news?
What in the hell is going on here?

1664
01:21:53,474 --> 01:21:56,910
I'm having another baby.

1665
01:21:59,346 --> 01:22:01,610
Mr. X:
...virtually impossible.

1666
01:22:01,649 --> 01:22:03,378
Mrs. X:
What exactly do you want?

1667
01:22:03,417 --> 01:22:06,181
Mr. X: And now my mother is here
so I can't go to Chicago.

1668
01:22:06,220 --> 01:22:08,518
Mrs. X:
One lousy week!

1669
01:22:08,555 --> 01:22:11,490
