1677
01:22:33,013 --> 01:22:34,776
Hmm.

1678
01:22:34,816 --> 01:22:37,979
Make it snappy, dear.
I'm on the last chapter.

1679
01:22:38,018 --> 01:22:40,077
Oh, thanks a million.

1680
01:22:53,634 --> 01:22:56,603
Oh.
You look gorgeous.

