to let her go.

1687
01:23:17,291 --> 01:23:19,782
Grayer:
I saw another one.

1688
01:23:19,828 --> 01:23:21,819
Annie:
Make a wish, Grove.

1689
01:23:21,863 --> 01:23:25,799
I wish we could stay
in 'Tucket forever,

1690
01:23:25,833 --> 01:23:29,200
Mommy, Daddy, you
and my puppy.

1691
01:23:36,176 --> 01:23:38,167
Grove?

1692
01:23:42,917 --> 01:23:46,045
You know I...

1693
01:23:46,086 --> 01:23:49,317
