your nanny forever.

1694
01:23:49,356 --> 01:23:52,450
I can't be.

1695
01:23:52,493 --> 01:23:55,929
That doesn't mean I'm not
gonna always be your friend.

1696
01:24:19,888 --> 01:24:22,789
What, there's no OJ
in the god-damned shit-shack?

1697
01:24:22,824 --> 01:24:25,725
Oh, I was just
about to make some.

1698
01:24:25,760 --> 01:24:27,489
Mm-hm.

1699
01:24:36,671 --> 01:24:39,572
Where's Grayer?
Isn't he up yet?

1700
01:24:39,606 --> 01:24:42,837
Um, he had a little
trouble sleeping.

1701
01:24:42,877 --> 01:24:44,708
So...

1702
01:24:48,682 --> 01:24:52,049
Concentrate? You have
got to be kidding me.

1703
01:24:52,086 --> 01:24:55,283
All my money and I can't
get fresh-squeezed? Come on.

1704
01:24:55,322 --> 01:24:57,051
[chuckles]

1705
01:24:57,091 --> 01:25:00,390
Uh, we used it all
at the party, so...

1706
01:25:00,427 --> 01:25:02,156
Hmm.

1707
01:25:02,196 --> 01:25:05,688
Well then, why don't you and I
take a little trip to the market

